---
---
<section id="dresscode" class="dresscode-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Dresscode</h2>
    <div class="section-divider reveal"><span>✦</span></div>

    <p class="dresscode-tag reveal">Elegante Formal</p>
    <p class="dresscode-intro reveal">
      Nos encantaría que vinierais elegantes para estar a la altura del ambiente del día.<br/>
      Aquí os dejamos algunas indicaciones:
    </p>

    <div class="dresscode-grid reveal">
      <div class="dresscode-card">
        <div class="dresscode-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
            <path d="M12 4 L6 10 L10 12 L10 32 L26 32 L26 12 L30 10 L24 4"/>
            <path d="M12 4 Q18 8 24 4"/>
            <path d="M18 8 L18 14"/>
            <circle cx="18" cy="16" r="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Ellos</h3>
        <p>Traje oscuro o esmoquin.<br/>Corbata o pajarita.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="dresscode-card">
        <div class="dresscode-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
            <path d="M11 4 Q18 2 25 4 L28 10 L22 12 L22 32 L14 32 L14 12 L8 10 Z"/>
            <path d="M14 12 Q18 16 22 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Ellas</h3>
        <p>Vestido largo o de cóctel.<br/>Tacón o sandalia elegante.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dresscode-avoid reveal">
      <span class="dresscode-avoid-icon" aria-hidden="true">✕</span>
      <p>Por favor, evitad el <strong>blanco</strong> y el <strong>negro puro</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dresscode-section {
    padding: var(--section-padding);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .dresscode-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .dresscode-intro {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .dresscode-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .dresscode-card {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .dresscode-icon {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .dresscode-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .dresscode-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .dresscode-avoid {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 0.7rem 1.6rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .dresscode-avoid-icon {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #c0392b;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .dresscode-avoid strong { color: var(--color-text); }

  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    .dresscode-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 300px; }
  }
</style>
